


#################        zOeCher Bot 6.x Edition     #####################

    ****** REQUIRED Packages *****
    1) Python 2.7.x
    2) Twisted 12.0.0 or higher
    3) git-core
    4) Sqlite3
################
    
    rename config file in settings dir (simple_config.py to config.py)
    then run zoecher.py
    
    to add zoecher bot to auto start system
    copy zoecher.sh to /etc/init.d/zoecher
    then type:
	update-rc.d zoecher defaults
	
	service zoecher start
	service zoecher stop
	
	
